    <item>
      <title>One Cigarette Butt Per</title>
      <link>https://bick-jp.github.io/project/one-cigarette-butt-per/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Dec 2016 16:18:30 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bick-jp.github.io/project/one-cigarette-butt-per/</guid>
      <description>&lt;p&gt;I walked 2.649km and picked up 618 littered cigarette butts in Tokyo. On average, there was one cigarette butt for every 2.07 square meters. The line drawn with charcoal is the exact trace of my walking route.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Date: December 2016&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Material: Craft Paper, Cigarette Butts, Charcoal&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;Size: 100cm&lt;em&gt;207cm, 207cm&lt;/em&gt;207cm, 61.8cm*61.8cm&lt;/p&gt;
</description>
    </item>
    
    <item>
      <title>Kumano Daigaku</title>
      <link>https://bick-jp.github.io/project/kumano-daigaku/</link>
      <pubDate>Thu, 22 Dec 2016 16:09:39 -0500</pubDate>
      <guid>https://bick-jp.github.io/project/kumano-daigaku/</guid>
